{
  "stem": "23350.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had no clothes, but it had a little cupboard for clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it had a-- an iron bed, a little carpet, and then, of course, we were brought in to be-- and we were pampered.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me, and they washed my hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember they washed my hair with soap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was Pearl soap-- [LAUGHS] --like today, whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave me a bath.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- I was so cozy and nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I went to bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was lovely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the next day-- the next day we went-- we had an enormous dining room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the dining room was only for 150 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we-- they would-- took it in two sessions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember we went for the first session into the dining room, and they brought these big lorries with bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the bread was so big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've never seen such big bread, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, white bread-- and they didn't have machinery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were cutting it by hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they couldn't cut-- even how many people-- they couldn't cut as many pieces as we needed to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the boys, they were hiding the bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As soon as it came on the table, they put it in here somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The bread was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they're shouting, more bread!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "More bread!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then the food arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "More food!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Oh, they were so thin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, you can see from the picture, from that main picture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were all very hungry people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was in Windermere the longest with this other girl, Rosarela, and some other boys, because we were sent to the sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The others were all sent to different hostels.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The girls were sent to Manchester.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They could study.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They could do.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
